{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Do you even know cross entropy?","date":"06-04-2019"},"html":"<p>Ok so this is a bit embarrassing. A friend asked me this question when explaining some concepts in this Big Data class I was taking at the time. Although I have learned entropy in my physics, computer engineering, and probability classes, I was unable to explain what it was. Honestly, the thought of entropy, cross entropy, and KL divergence used to scare me...it just sounds so technical. However, engineers just love to make easy things seem difficult!</p>\n<p>Below is an explanation of the three easiest concepts on earth:</p>\n<h2>Entropy</h2>\n<p>h<sub>θ</sub>(x) = θ<sub>o</sub> x + θ<sub>1</sub>x</p>\n<p>$a^2 + b^2 = c^2$</p>\n<p>H(y) = Σ y log <sup>1</sup>⁄<sub>y</sub></p>\n<p>&#x26;frac1y;</p>\n<h2>Cross entropy</h2>\n<h2>KL Divergence</h2>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 750px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 102.64279624893436%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"kb\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/81d0cab134735c9fcc6536ab49f61e6b/a66cd/kb.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/81d0cab134735c9fcc6536ab49f61e6b/4272c/kb.jpg 188w,\n/static/81d0cab134735c9fcc6536ab49f61e6b/1459e/kb.jpg 375w,\n/static/81d0cab134735c9fcc6536ab49f61e6b/a66cd/kb.jpg 750w,\n/static/81d0cab134735c9fcc6536ab49f61e6b/c0626/kb.jpg 1125w,\n/static/81d0cab134735c9fcc6536ab49f61e6b/080b2/kb.jpg 1173w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"p1"}}